Slack,the,team,collaboration,and,messaging,chat,app,hosts,the,Slack,Real,Time,Messaging,RTM,API,for,embedding,real,time,chat,functionality,within,clients,This,WebSocket,based,API,enables,developers,to,programmatically,receive,events,as,well,as,send,messages,using,Slack,in,real,time,Once,connected,the,server,will,provide,a,continuous,stream,of,events,recent,messages,and,updates,made,to,the,Slack,team,The,websocket,connection,uses,JSON,for,requests,and,responses,and,uses,OAuth,for,authentication